msgid "Display dialog boxes from shell scripts"
msgstr "Vis dialogbokse fra skal-scripts"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.kdialog.metainfo.xml:9
msgid ""
"KDialog allows you to display dialog boxes from shell scripts. The syntax is "
"very much inspired from the \"dialog\" command (which shows text mode "
"dialogs)."
msgstr ""
"Med KDialog kan man vise dialogbokse fra skal-scripts. Syntaksen er meget "
"inspireret af \"dialog\"-kommandoen (som viser dialoger i tekstform)."
